VALUES
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00039', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '小丁是財富的風險愛好者（risklover），則下列何者正確？', '["小丁財富的邊際效用會隨著財富的增加而遞減", "小丁財富的邊際效用不會隨著財富的增加而改變", "小丁財富的邊際效用會隨著財富的增加而遞增", "小丁財富的邊際效用會隨著財富的增加先遞減再遞增"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00040', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '考慮一個經濟體系包含了兩個消費者、兩個生產要素以及兩個廠商。則此經濟體系的契約曲線 （contractcurve）會滿足下列何種條件？', '["在契約曲線上的每一點，必為兩個消費者無異曲線的相交點", "在契約曲線上的每一點，必有一個生產要素沒有用完", "在契約曲線上的每一點，必是該經濟體系最有效率的分配組合點", "在契約曲線上的每一點，必滿足第二社會福利定理"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00041', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設在一個完全競爭市場裡，整體廠商生產X的邊際成本為0.2X，同時每增加1單位X產生的 污染物所造成的社會損害成本為2元，消費者對X的需求曲線為P=6-0.2X，若政府以課污染稅的 方式欲使外部成本內部化，則每單位X應課之從量稅及此時之產量為何？', '["（1,10）", "（1,20）", "（2,20）", "（2,10） 32260 32760"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00042', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲國國民生產雞蛋並提供電影娛樂服務。一年內，他們生產了價值 1,000 萬元的雞蛋，其中 800 萬元的雞蛋供國內所需，另外200萬元的雞蛋外銷至乙國。甲國國民在國內外共提供了價值500 萬元的電影娛樂服務，其中在甲國提供價值200萬元，在乙國提供價值300萬元。此外，他們從 乙國購買了價值400萬元的天然氣。下列敘述何者正確？', '["國民生產毛額（GNP）為1,000萬元", "國內生產毛額（GDP）為1,500萬元", "出口淨額（netexports）為100萬元", "經常帳餘額（currentaccountbalance）為100萬元"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1"], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00043', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '當緊縮缺口存在時，根據附加預期的菲力普曲線（expectations-augmentedPhillipscurve），下列何 者正確？', '["預期通貨膨脹率大於實際通貨膨脹率", "預期通貨膨脹率等於實際通貨膨脹率", "預期通貨膨脹率小於實際通貨膨脹率", "預期通貨膨脹率與實際通貨膨脹率的關係不確定"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00044', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '梭羅模型（Solow model）假設生產函數具有規模報酬不變（constant return to scale）的性質。若 Y、K、L分別代表產出、資本與勞動，則下列生產函數何者不具有規模報酬不變的性質？', '["Y=K0.3L0.7", "Y=KL", "Y= KL", "Y=K+L"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00045', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一修正凱因斯模型如下： 消費函數：C(Y－T)=0.8(Y－T)； 投資需求函數：I=306－28r； 政府支出：G=0； 稅收函數：T=T +0.1Y，T =0；', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00046', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '0 實質貨幣需求函數：Ld=Y－100r； 實質貨幣供給額：1,000元。 如果政府決定改增加人頭稅（T ）10元，以做公共支出之用時，則均衡所得為何？ 0', '["850元", "950元", "1,050元", "1,150元"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 0, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00047', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '當發生流動性陷阱時，下列何者正確？', '["財政支出的增加不會對廠商投資產生排擠效應", "公開市場買入債券，帶動產出增加", "調降重貼現率，增加商品需求", "財政支出的增加，不存在產出效果"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-00048', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc', 'heelevel3-d30bcefc-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-heelevel3-d30bcefc-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '當短期總合供給曲線愈陡峭時，則菲利普曲線（Phillipscurve）：', '["愈平坦", "愈陡峭", "愈向後彎曲", "與短期總合供給曲線的斜率無關"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5eb67721d51d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "0e7bbb6b55ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113080", "c": "319", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "企業管理"}'::jsonb, NULL)
